overview:
ProGamingAustralia.com is a financial transaction platform that allows Aussies to wager real cash on their video game matches.

Supporting PS3, Xbox 360, PC and Nintendo Wii, ProGamingAustralia.com allows its members to compete 1v1 or Team Battles on the latest and most popular game titles including Call of Duty, Fifa Soccer, Street Fighter and hundreds more.

Have you got the skills to pay the bills? Get involved and register an account at www.ProGamingAustralia.com
